    },
    {
      "number": 6102,
      "number_in_surah": 4,
      "text_arabic": "لَقَدْ خَلَقْنَا ٱلْإِنسَٰنَ فِىٓ أَحْسَنِ تَقْوِيمٍۢ",
      "text_translation": "We have certainly created man in the best of stature;",
