      "text_arabic": "إِلَّا ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُوا۟ وَعَمِلُوا۟ ٱلصَّٰلِحَٰتِ فَلَهُمْ أَجْرٌ غَيْرُ مَمْنُونٍۢ",
      "text_translation": "Except for those who believe and do righteous deeds, for they will have a reward uninterrupted.",
